{"tid":1910105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山崎漂白水淋賣剩包阻拾荒者執食被斥折墮","createTime":"2020-03-04T12:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T12:24:04.000Z","uid":67500,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0055ef61078e184cfb28083902bc5b24d051be86","tid":1910105,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T12:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120628/16466724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120628%2F16466724&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIF7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=66a9352a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120628%2F16466724&h=7dab7d6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20120628/16466724</a><br />\n<br />\n記者本月多次到訪山崎麵飽位於油塘的分店，發現每晚10時關門後，店員即半拉下電子閘，並將賣剩的麪包掃到垃圾袋內。稍後有店員拿着漂白水走往麪包架，向垃圾袋內淋漂白水，包好後即交予早在門外等候的港鐵清潔員。記者追蹤發現，這些「垃圾」會被丟棄在港鐵站附近的小型垃圾收集站。記者待清潔員離開後察看，即使尚未打開垃圾袋，已嗅到濃烈漂白水味道。打開袋後，麪包已沾滿漂白水，不能進食。"},{"pid":"1311a9eb3ae91e23199a23228ae7c96438699100","tid":1910105,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T12:17:19.000Z","msg":"到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1909951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1909951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4a003365aaf21b09766487bb416fd6f90c2ba70","tid":1910105,"uid":333259,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"好多連鎖超市都係咁，因為如果啲人食左被拋棄既食物而唔舒服，間店舖要負上責任，所以整到啲人食唔到先可以保護自己，冇話折唔折墮嘅..."}]}